	<name translatable='no'>PinApp</name>
	<summary>Create and edit application shortcuts</summary>
    <developer_name translatable="no">Fabrizio Alberio</developer_name>
	<description>
	  <p>PinApp is a simple application that lets you customize your app list.</p>
	  <p>Some of the possible uses are</p>
	  <ul>
		<li>Changing an app icon that doesn't fit in with your theme</li>
		<li>Creating custom shortcuts to websites</li>
		<li>Hiding apps you don't want to see</li>
		<li>Editing properties in .desktop files</li>
	  </ul>
	  <p>The app is made with Libadwaita and GTK4, with consideration for small-screen devices</p>
	</description>
